Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,路西菲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}總之 好像是緊急事態啊
